# .env
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Lighthouse Talent — PUBLIC client config (safe to commit).
# These VITE_* vars are inlined into the browser bundle by Vite,
# so they are public by design. dotenvx encrypts the values at rest;
# decryption needs the private key in .env.keys (gitignored).
#
# Run via:  npm run dev   (scripts are wrapped in `dotenvx run`)
# NEVER put a secret (service_role, DB password, any token) in here.
# Operational secrets live in .env.ops.local (gitignored, local-only).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
